Class Objective

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.core.model.CardGame
it.polimi.ingsw.core.model.Card
it.polimi.ingsw.core.model.Objective
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
PositionObjective, ResourceObjective
public class Objective extends Card implements Serializable
This class represents an Objective in the game. It extends the Card class and implements Serializable interface. It maintains the points, type, completion status, and other related data.
